INSERT INTO `quest_request_items` (`ID`, `EmoteOnComplete`, `EmoteOnIncomplete`, `EmoteOnCompleteDelay`, `EmoteOnIncompleteDelay`, `CompletionText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES
('30300','0','0','0','0','I\'d rather die than live as a mogu prisoner. They are not kind captors.','0'),
('30481','0','0','0','0','You find stones for Rook? Please?','0'),
('38688','0','0','0','0','   , $n?','21249'),
('41891','0','0','0','0','I hope you are not intentionally slowing my search, $r.','21021'),
('45753','0','0','0','0','A diamond ring? Why... why are you bringing this to me?','0'),
('45758','0','0','0','0','You wrote me a song? How thoughtful.','0'),
('45762','0','0','0','0','What have we here?','0'),
('46062','0','0','0','0','Mrglr?','0'),
('46125','1','0','0','0','If I have more resources at my disposal, I can prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapon. $b$bLeave these resources to me as soon as possible! The Legion must fall!','23420'),
('46148','1','0','0','0','   -...       ,               .$b$b                ,   .$b$b      !   !','24015'),
('46149','1','0','0','0','If I have more resources at my disposal, I can prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapon. $b$bLeave these resources to me as soon as possible! The Legion must fall!','23360'),
('46150','1','0','0','0','If I have more of the Order\'s resources at my disposal, I will be able to prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapons. This knowledge will help you to saturate your weapons with a power that nothing can compare to. Bring me those resources as soon as possible! We\'re going to win!','23360'),
('46151','1','0','0','0','If I have more of the Order\'s resources at my disposal, I will prepare a new collection of records for you about the history and potential of your weapons. Bring me those resources as soon as possible! The Legion must fall!','23360'),
('46152','0','0','0','0','With even more order resources, I can scribe further notes about your artifact weapon\'s history and potential.$B$BThis knowledge will be crucial for infusing your weapon with additional power.$B$BBring me those resources as soon as you can. The Legion will cry out in agony as they die!','0'),
('46153','1','0','0','0','If I have more resources at my disposal, I will be able to prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapon. The Legion must fall!','23360'),
('46154','0','0','0','0','With even more order resources, I can scribe further notes about your artifact weapon\'s history and potential.$B$BThis knowledge will be crucial for infusing your weapon with additional power.$B$BBring me those resources as soon as you can. Balance must be restored!','0'),
('46156','1','0','0','0','If I have more of the Order\'s resources at my disposal, I can prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapons. From them, you\'ll know how to add even more power to your artifact. Give me those resources as soon as possible! The Legion must fall!','23420'),
('46157','1','0','0','0','If I have more of the Order\'s resources at my disposal, I can prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapons. You have no idea how much interesting it is! Bring me those resources as soon as possible. There\'s a great wisdom in words - you just have to see it.','23360'),
('46158','1','0','0','0','If I have more of the Order\'s resources at my disposal, I can prepare another set of records for you about the history and potential of your weapons.You\'ll learn from them how to add more power to your artifact. May the winds show us the way to victory!','23420');
INSERT INTO `quest_offer_reward` (`ID`, `Emote1`, `Emote2`, `Emote3`, `Emote4`, `EmoteDelay1`, `EmoteDelay2`, `EmoteDelay3`, `EmoteDelay4`, `RewardText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES
('30233','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Yes! Only one Cracklefang remains to terrorize the goats and yaks of the Vale of Eternal Blossoms. As it should be! Thank you for that!$B$BI sure hope no more big nasty wolves turn up. I really don\'t think I\'m going to be able to come up with another name that can live up to that one.','0'),
('30234','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','My staff! My gorgeous staff! We shall never part again. I shall lean on you, and you will always be there. And I promise not to poke crocodiles with you anymore.$B$BThank you, friend. Your staff retrieval skills have proved invaluable today!','0'),
('30235','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','For the sake of the villagers, I hope he remains at bay for some time.$B$BThank you, my friend.','0'),
('30236','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','The spirits may be childlike, but they possess generous mounts of strength for their size. Your victory is no small thing, and is very appreciated.','0'),
('30239','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Lao-Fe the Slavebinder was one of the most spiteful and vicious mogu of his time. May defeating his spirit act as a reminder to all the mogu in the vale of the fate that awaits them if they seek to defile the sacred pools again.$B$BYour strength is unquestionable. You have my respect, $C.','0'),
('30244','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','The mantid forces on the wall have been thinned.','0'),
('30248','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Look at you! All proactive and assertive. Looks good on you.','0'),
('30296','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Leader gone. People safe. Rook save village. And friend save village too. Thank you, friend!','0'),
('30297','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Leader gone. People safe. Rook save village. And friend save village too. Thank you, friend!','0'),
('30298','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Their foothold in these ruins shall not last the night.','0'),
('30299','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Your efforts here make all the difference. Thank you so much for your help, friend.','0'),
('30300','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Many of those you saved are back here in camp recovering. You surely have their gratitude, and mine.','0'),
('30301','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Smoke in the distance tells me that you were successful. Good work, $C.','0'),
('30302','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','You haven\'t let me down. I won\'t forget that.','0'),
('30305','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','You really good friend. Rook like you. Thank you, good friend!','0'),
('30481','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','So many! And so shiny! You did real good!$B$BThank you, little friend. Rook like you a lot.','0'),
('31136','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Well fought. I hope to see more of you soon.','0'),
('31240','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Good, you\'re here.$B$BFor a while there, I was wondering if Ren would even deliver the message.','0'),
('31244','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Glad you\'re here. Let\'s get to work.','0'),
('31245','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Ren send you my way? He puts on playful air, but he follows through when it matters. Can\'t hold it against him much.','0'),
('31246','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','You come to help Rook?','0'),
('31247','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Well timed. I was just about to go put some recruits through their paces, but I\'d be much more eager to see what you have to offer.','0'),
('31249','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','It is strange to be dispatched away from the combat, but Leven is right in that the villagers need our protection. We cannot afford any risks.','0'),
('31295','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Good to see you.$B$BI don\'t know where the mogu mustered all these forces, but we need to hit them hard before they can push their advantage.','0'),
('31296','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Sun is smart to send me the strong ones. I\'d accept nothing else.','0'),
('35172','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','We look forward to serving you again.','0'),
('38688','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0',',    ,      ,        .','21249'),
('38992','1','66','0','0','0','500','0','0','        ,      .          .$b$b         ,  .','21287'),
('40992','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Your skills are... impressive. If it matters at all, I would have taken no pleasure in killing you.$B$BLook, I\'m no fool - noone in their right mind would willingly choose death. I\'ve yet to see what the others clearly see in you, but hey -$B$BAt least I know you can fight.','21108'),
('41102','1','1','66','0','0','0','0','0','With each day that passes I see more of Lord Illidan in you, Master $n. You have sacrificed more than any... and the war is far from over.$B$BWe may not see eye to eye at times, but I trust your capability to lead us to finish our mission - no matter the cost.$B$BNo Illidari in your command is as capable as I, if you ever require my skills just say the word and consider it done.','20994'),
('41891','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','','21232'),
('42003','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0',' ,   ? ,   .$B$B-  -      .      ,          ,   .$B$B      .       ,   .      ,      ','21267'),
('44091','396','396','0','0','0','0','0','0','An attack on the gates of Orgrimmar! Thank goodness you defended the Warchief!$b$bI must inform the Council of Six at once. This is grave news indeed.$b$bPlease, feel free to look around Dalaran. The advantage you seek against the Legion just might turn up.','21737'),
('45753','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Ah, a sigil. From the Abyssal High Council, no less!$B$B<Warlord Gorchuk wipes a bead of sweat from his brow.>$B$BI... I had assumed that it was... that you were... oh, never mind.$B$BFor the Horde!','0'),
('45758','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Ah, I see, it is a hard-earned reward from one of your many battles. Well done, $C!','0'),
('45762','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','A sigil from the Abyssal High Council? You\'ve outdone yourself today, $R.$B$BFor the Alliance!','0'),
('46062','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Glrrrrms!','0'),
('46064','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','Mrrga mr. Gll-mrrr!','0'),
